title: Primovist® Liver MRI
description:
The template covers the examination of single or multiple liver lesions. Surrounding organ structures such as biliary tracts and lymph nodes are also covered. 

Primovist® is approved for the detection and characterization of focal liver lesions using T1-weighted magnetic resonance imaging (MRI). Further Information:
https://radiology.bayer.com/products-and-services/mri/contrast-agents/primovist
